<br>

＜Think88's Blog＞さん<br>
<a href="http://think88.wordpress.com/2011/02/14/mac%E3%81%A7win7-part-2-vmware-fusion-3-1-2-%E3%83%AC%E3%83%93%E3%83%A5%E3%83%BC/" target="_blank">MacでWin7! Part-2 VMware Fusion 3.1.2 レビュー</a><br>
